reviews: Easy to search for specific items and see which auctions they will be on. Simply type in what you're looking for example: Case 1250 and see what auctions they will be on! Also great to be able to browse auctions on the map that are close to me and check out the complete auction lineup.
From Western Nebraska and no auctions in my area. No way to search for specific machinery. If you want a disk, or combine, ect. You have to search each auction individually.
